name: Jordyn Jones (LoRA)
description:
Jordyn Jones

I was shocked to see (shocked I tell you) there was no LoRA for Jordyn Jones. So I'm here to fill that void in all your lives. Jordyn is famous for being hot. That's about it.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!

I used 40 pictures from her instagram and elsewhere, 50 steps each, kohya_ss defaults.

She looks best between 0.6-0.9 but even full strength works on occasion, ymmv. Strength grids included in my sample images.
